## P4 — Job ingestion → JobPost artifacts (paste-first)
**Architecture mapping:** L1 + L2 + L4 (simulated Job Understanding)  
**Purpose:** Turn raw job descriptions into structured JobPost artifacts.

### Inputs
- Job description text pasted in UI (3 job posts recommended)

### Processing
- Deterministic extraction: title, required skills list (keyword list), location, constraints

### Outputs
- `outputs/jobs/job_post_v1_<timestamp>.json` (one per job)

### Example (Tanish)
He pastes 3 jobs:
1) GenAI Engineer (Python + RAG + vector DB)
2) ML Engineer (Kubernetes + MLflow + CI/CD)
3) Solution Architect (AWS + Docker + governance)

Each becomes a JobPost artifact.

